2. Changelog
------------
This is a non-exhaustive (but still near complete) changelog for the Joomla
Platform project, including alpha and beta versions.  Our thanks to all those
people who've contributed bug reports and code fixes.

Legend:

* -> Security Fix
# -> Issue Fix
$ -> Language fix or change
+ -> Addition
^ -> Change
- -> Removed
! -> Note


27-Feb-2011 Louis Landry
 + JLog package.

8-Feb-2011 Louis Landry
 + Added simple HTTP client library.

5-Feb-2011 Louis Landry
 ! Initiate work on Joomla Platform project.
 ^ Reworked JVersion, JLoader and the initial import script for the platform project.
 ^ Moved the example configuration file into the root libraries folder.
 ^ Added libraries and tests top level folders for clean separation.
 ^ Changed file headers to remove the subversion tags and clean up the rest.
